# Docs & plans

**Locations:** `docs/architecture/` (system, handoff), `docs/schemas/` (stable human schema; truth in code), `docs/analyses/` (temporary). History: `docs/plans/avklarat/`; `docs/old/` is pointer only. Full policy: `docs/architecture/archive/pre-2026-03-consolidation/documentation-lifecycle.md` (kanoniska översikter: `docs/architecture/README.md`).

**Plans:** `docs/plans/active/` → `review-needed/` → `avklarat/`. One canonical copy; archive when done. On status change: `docs/plans/README.md`, `docs/architecture/README.md` (handoff-historik: arkiv `agent-roadmap-and-handoff.md`), folder README.

**Structural / terminology / flow changes:** Update canonical files in the same turn; replace stale docs instead of duplicating; new file only for genuinely new scope. Renames: also `terminology.mdc`, `docs/`, `docs/ENV.md` if paths matter, `scripts/README.md` if scripts/artifacts change. Larger write-ups → `docs/architecture/` + link from `docs/README.md`.
